{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"故今日他在這裡沒有一個親戚。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"除膿汁外，他沒有食物。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"只有迷誤的人們才吃膿汁。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"不然！我以你們所能見的萬象盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"並且以你們不能見的幽玄盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"這確是尊貴的使者的言辭；"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"並不是詩人的言辭，你們很少信仰，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"也不是僕人的言辭，你們很少覺悟。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"這是從全世界的主降示的。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"假若他假借我的名義，捏造謠言，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"我必以權力逮捕他，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"然後必割斷他的大動脈，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"你們中沒有一個人能保衛他。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"這確是對敬畏者的教訓。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"我的確知道你們中有否認的人。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"這對於不信道的人們確是悔恨。"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"這確是真實的信念，"},{"SurahNumber":69,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"故你當頌揚你的主的大名。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"有人曾請求一種將發生的刑罰。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"那是為不信的人們而預定的，沒有任何人能加以抵抗。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"那是真主——天梯的主宰——發出的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"眾天神和精神在一日之內升到他那裡。那一日的長度是五萬年。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你安然地忍受吧。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他們以為那刑罰是很遠的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"我卻以為那是很近的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日天像熔銅，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"山像彩絨。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"親戚相見不相同。"}]}